You are analyzing code for **XML External Entity (XXE)** vulnerabilities.

## What Is XXE?

XXE occurs when an XML parser processes user-supplied XML input with external entity resolution enabled. An attacker can craft XML with malicious entity definitions to read arbitrary server files (`file:///etc/passwd`), perform SSRF, cause denial of service via entity expansion (billion laughs), or in some cases achieve remote code execution.

